1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Family psychologist Sergey Vasnetsov is in trouble. His wife left him leaving five daughters and mother-in-law. The eldest daughter, Masha, is windy fashionista; the second daughter, Darya, is goth; the third daughter, Evgeniya, is athlete; the fourth daughter, Galina, is an A student and the youngest daughter, Polina, is a little baby. All are very noisy. And none of them know how to clean and cook. On top of that, Vasnetsov lately has no luck with customers.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Sergey Vasnetsov got his first and only customer. It's Oksana Fedotova who is unhappy wife of Rublyovka's oligarch. Meanwhile, the daughters try to cook and clean the apartment by themselves for the first time.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Sergey learns that Masha is dating two guys at the same time and it's shocking him. And Galina Sergeevna is joining a new grade where Dasha is studying.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Vasnetsov doesn't like that his daughters can't find a common language with each other, and he decides to spend a session of psychotherapy with them. And then there are problems with his mother-in-law: Grandma refuses to look after Pugovka when he at work.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Learning that Dasha likes to go to gothic parties with her friends Pauk (Spider) and Cherep (Skull), Vasnetsov tries to understand her passion and as a result almost fails the session of psychotherapy with Oksana. In the meantime, Masha and Zhenya are changing roles in order to get to know each other better: they go to football and then to the club together for the first time.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: All five of Vasnetsov's daughters suddenly needed money to buy clothes. And also the grandmother demands the salary for preparation of girls for receipt on biological faculty.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Vasnetsov's best friend, dentist Andrey Antonov, believes that by giving so much time to his daughters, Sergey loses his masculinity and authority. And the sisters help grandmother to find a stranger named Murzik.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Masha is invited to appear on TV show but the role isn't the best. Sergey met a teacher Lyudmila Mikhaylovna who falls in love with him. He decides to get rid of her, as a result of which Galina Sergeyevna gets the bad mark for the first time.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Vasnetsov misses the long-awaited meeting with his friends in order to go to the play in which his daughters play. Masha, Dasha and Galina Sergeyevna are arguing who played the best there.

10.title: Ziganka
10.plot: Pugovka asks dad the question: "What if you are not my dad?", after which he proves by all means and falsities to the children his kinship with them. Meanwhile, the sisters find his resemblance to grandma.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Because of Antonov's nightly romance, Vasnetsov has to do repair in the apartment. Sisters begin to excruciate the conscience because of the "borrowed" from grandmother five thousand rubles.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Sergey doesn't like that Pugovka copies grandma in all she do. And he decides that she should spend time with her peers, and needs to be arranged in a kindergarten. However, problems arise with this. Galina Sergeyevna meanwhile is getting ready for a contest from the Ministry of Education.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Sisters suddenly remember that it's father's birthday. An interesting situation: they think that Dad has forgotten about it, and he himself thinks that his daughters have forgotten about his birthday.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: It seems to Vasnetsov that he is an unwanted old ruin for nobody because he was mistaken for Pugovka's grandfather in the kindergarten. It also turns out that the ideal in everything Galina Sergeyevna can't sing.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: Sergey's office was on fire, and he invited his rich client to his own home. After that Oksana will begin to doubt whether she wants a child.

16.title: Episode #1.16
16.plot: Vasnetsov offers Oksana a new method of psychotherapy called "children therapy". The method is simple: she must look after his daughters.

17.title: Episode #1.17
17.plot: Educational activities initiated by Vasnetsov on the occasion of the end of his daughters' study quarter, fails. Dasha leaves home.

18.title: Episode #1.18
18.plot: Sergey caught flu; Oksana receives care of him. And at the same time, the sisters are looking after the grandma's flat feeding her spiders and tidying up the apartment.

19.title: Episode #1.19
19.plot: There a love drama in The Vasnetsov Family: Zhenya starts an affair with classmate Vova, and her father is in love with his client. But both this relationships can be destroyed because Zhenya is going to leave for a sports board for a month, and Oksana and her husband are leaving for London, and, perhaps, for forever.

20.title: Episode #1.20
20.plot: Vasnetsov is tormented by his conscience because he deceived his favorite client Oksana. At this time, the sisters prepare a surprise for their father intending to celebrate The Family Day.

1.title: Episode #2.1
1.plot: Vasnetsov wants to abandon co-called "children therapy" and to confess to Oksana he lied her; Vasiliy insists on continuing the sessions. While Sergey and Antonov trying to cope with the secretary's dog all day who doesn't let them leave the office, the second grandma comes to the sisters - from the paternal side. Between grandmas begins serious competition for the love of granddaughters. The next day, Oksana becomes angry with Dad: she learned that children therapy is a complete deception.

2.title: Episode #2.2
2.plot: Daughters learn that Dad deceived everyone by inventing children therapy and they boycott him. Sergey is afraid to go home and stay up late at work. And the daughters are frightened: maybe they weren't right with starting a boycott. Grandma makes her granddaughters swallow a garlic clove every day but they discover a remedy that is much tastier than garlic and helps better in the prevention of influenza.

3.title: Episode #2.3
3.plot: Galina Sergeyevna got an insulting nickname from her classmates. She tries different methods to get rid of it but without success. Sergey tries to get Oksana's forgiveness for his involuntary deception. And then there are angry customers threatening to avenge that he advised them in everything and always tell the truth.

4.title: Episode #2.4
4.plot: A new guy entered into Dasha's class. She falls in love with him and even refuses the Gothic style in clothes in order to please him. Sergey loses his head from love and longing for Oksana because of what goes to the reception to the therapist.

5.title: Episode #2.5
5.plot: Vasnetsov decides to move to live in the village in order to forget Oksana. But DAd's idea meets fierce resistance in the face of his daughters. Girls are not enthusiastic about the village life.

6.title: Episode #2.6
6.plot: Oksana has separated from her husband and left her Rublevka's house. Now she doesn't need anything but long-awaited freedom. Her husband froze her bank account, all those whom she considered friends turned away from her. Oksana has nowhere to live, and she comes to Vasnetsov.

7.title: Episode #2.7
7.plot: Sergey offers one of his five daughters to move in with grandma to make one room in the house empty for Oksana who in the meantime is looking for work on the ad. As a result, the new work, even if it turned out to be a fake, frees Vasnetsov's apartment from a lot of the things.

8.title: Episode #2.8
8.plot: Vasnetsov has to have a psychotherapy session with the headmistress of the school where his daughters are studying. He becomes aware of the secrets and love intrigues of all the teachers. And Oksana remains at home to look after Pugovka.

9.title: Episode #2.9
9.plot: Dasha was arrested. Dad hurries to the rescue and he was arrested himself. And Vasnetsov's clients all day are served by his faithful friend Antonov and Oksana.

10.title: Episode #2.10
10.plot: It turns out that Galina Sergeyevna is also capable of strong feelings. However, the subject of her adoration, classmate Ilya Polezhaykin, renders signs of attention to Masha. Galina Sergeyevna is jealous of him. And Oksana finally found a job - she got a job as a waitress in a restaurant.

11.title: Episode #2.11
11.plot: Vasnetsov finds Zhenya's diary, of course, reads it and learns a lot about himself. And Oksana got pestered by the cafe's director she works in. To get rid of this, she have to use a cunning move.

12.title: Episode #2.12
12.plot: Seeing Vasnetsov's hesitation towards Oksana, Antonov decides to date her and gives her a chic bouquet. And the school is experimenting: from the best students of the 10th grade will be formed a leadership class. Will Dasha and Polezhaykin now learn separately from Galina Sergeyevna?

13.title: Episode #2.13
13.plot: Sergey literally terrorized by all sorts of inspections. The aim of the inspectors is to close his private practice. Dasha feels all the "charms" of living together with grandma.

14.title: Episode #2.14
14.plot: Pugovka has got a dog. Vasnetsov got a client who suffers from compulsive buying disorder.

15.title: Episode #2.15
15.plot: Under the pressure, Zhenya had to play for the youth football team of her school. She even had a female fan, and very determined.
